@remark $VER: Y2kclock AmigaGuide« document v1.0 (15-Oct-99)

@node main "Y2k Clock v1.0 ® Joona I Palaste 1999"
"Y2k Clock" is a simple program to display the amount of seconds remaining to
Y2k (year 2000) in a digital form, with user-configurable colours, on any public
screen. It was written by me, Joona Palaste, in Amiga C in October 1999.

Ę @{"Installation" link "install"}
